<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;"><a href="/wiki/File:Wikibooks-logo-en.svg" class="image" title="Wikibooks logo"><img alt="Wikibooks logo" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7c/Wikibooks-logo-en.svg/14px-Wikibooks-logo-en.svg.png" width="14" height="14" border="0" /></a> <a href="http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Erlang_Programming" class="extiw" title="wikibooks:Erlang Programming">Erlang Programming</a> at <a href="/wiki/Wikibooks" title="Wikibooks">Wikibooks</a></td>
</tr>
